# Image Properties:
# - Format: PNG (Lossless compression)
# - Dimensions: 1242x2436 pixels (3x resolution)
# - Color Space: sRGB
# - Background Color: #1A1A1A (Dark theme)
# - Accent Color: #00FF88 (Neon)
# - File Size: <= 500KB
# - WCAG 2.1 Level AA Compliant (7:1 contrast ratio)

# Responsive Breakpoints:
# - Mobile S: 320px
# - Mobile L: 425px
# - Tablet: 768px
# - Desktop: 1024px

# Platform Support:
# - iOS: 14.0+ (iPhone SE, 8+, X+, iPad)
# - Android: API 21+ (mdpi to xxxhdpi)
# - Web: PNG + WebP formats

# Design Elements:
# - Logo Placement: Center
# - Background Style: Solid #1A1A1A
# - Animation: Fade (1000ms)
# - Safe Area Insets: All sides

# Optimization:
# - WebP conversion for web
# - Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
# - Load Time: < 200ms
# - Memory Impact: Minimal

# Image Generation Command:
# convert -size 1242x2436 xc:#1A1A1A \
#   -gravity center \
#   -fill "#00FF88" \
#   -draw "text 0,0 'Fantasy GM'" \
#   -quality 100 \
#   splash.png

# WebP Conversion:
# cwebp -q 100 splash.png -o splash.webp

# Verify Specifications:
# - identify -verbose splash.png
# - imagemagick -verify splash.png
# - lighthouse --only-categories=performance splash.png